#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Launching &kfind;"
msgstr "Pokretanje <application>K‑nalazača</application>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Find Files tool is a useful method of searching for specific files on "
"your computer, or for searching for files that match a pattern. An example "
"of this could include searching for files of a particular type or with "
"certain letters in the filename. You can load this utility in &konqueror; "
"(in file manager mode) by selecting <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find File</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the menu. If "
"you want to use &kfind; as a standalone search tool, launch it by using "
"&krunner;."
msgstr ""
"<application>K‑nalazač</application> je alatka za traženje određenih fajlova "
"na računaru po imenu, odnosno obrascu imena, i drugim atributima. Na primer, "
"mogu se tražiti fajlovi zadatog tipa, ili sa zadatim slovima u imenu fajla. "
"<application>K‑nalazač</application> možete pokrenuti iz "
"<application>K‑osvajača</application> (u režimu menadžera fajlova) izborom "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Ctrl</keycap> "
"<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>Alatke</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Nađi fajl...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz menija. Ako želite "
"da koristite <application>K‑nalazač</application> kao samostalnu alatku, "
"pokrenite ga <application>K‑izvođačem</application>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finding Files"
msgstr "Traženje fajlova"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Name/Location Tab"
msgstr "Jezičak <guilabel>Ime/lokacija</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When starting &kfind;, you will see a quite simple window. Type in the name "
"of the file you are searching for in the text box labeled <guilabel>Named:</"
"guilabel>. You can use wildcard matching and a semicolon (<quote>;</quote>) "
"for separating multiple names."
msgstr ""
"Po pokretanju <application>K‑nalazača</application> videćete sasvim "
"jednostavan prozor. Unesite ime fajla koji tražite u polje <guilabel>Po "
"imenu:</guilabel>. Možete koristiti džokere, kao i tačku-zarez za "
"razdvajanje više imena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose a folder where you want to search by typing it in the field "
"<guilabel>Look in:</guilabel> or by clicking <guibutton>Browse...</"
"guibutton> (you can toggle the display of the hidden files and folder in the "
"dialog using the shortcuts <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>.</"
"keycap></keycombo> or <keycap>F8</keycap>) and press &Enter; or click the "
"<guibutton>Find</guibutton> button. Use the <guibutton>Stop</guibutton> "
"button to cancel a search. A search result can be saved in &HTML; format or "
"as plain text with the <guibutton>Save As...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite fasciklu u kojoj će se tražiti unosom u polje <guilabel>Traži u:</"
"guilabel> ili klikom na <guibutton>Pregledaj...</guibutton> (skrivene "
"fajlove i fascikle možete prikazati i sakriti u dijalogu prečicom <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\"><keycap>Alt</keycap><keycap>.</keycap></keycombo> ili "
"<keycap>F8</keycap>), pa pritisnite <keycap>Enter</keycap> ili kliknite na "
"<guibutton>Nađi</guibutton>. Dugmetom <guibutton>Zaustavi</guibutton> "
"obustavljate pretragu. Rezultati pretrage mogu se sačuvati kao HTML ili "
"običan tekst, dugmetom <guibutton>Sačuvaj kao...</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Include subfolders</guilabel> is checked all subfolders "
"starting from your chosen folder will be searched too. If you enable "
"<guilabel>Case sensitive search</guilabel>, &kfind; will only find files "
"with the exact case matching names. Enable the option <guilabel>Show hidden "
"files</guilabel> to include them in your search. Selecting <guilabel>Use "
"files index</guilabel> lets you use the files' index created by the "
"<quote>locate</quote> package to speed-up the search."
msgstr ""
"Ako je popunjeno <guilabel>Uključi potfascikle</guilabel>, biće pretraženi i "
"sve potfascikle fascikle koju ste izabrali. Ako uključite <guilabel>Razlikuj "
"veličinu slova</guilabel>, <application>K‑nalazač</application> će uzeti u "
"obzir samo fajlove kod kojih se tačno poklapa veličina slova. Uključite "
"opciju <guilabel>Prikaži skrivene fajlove</guilabel> da i njih obuhvatite "
"pretragom. Popunjavanjem <guilabel>Koristi indeks fajlova</guilabel> "
"nalažete da se koristi indeks fajlova koji se pravi za naredbu "
"<command>locate</command>, radi ubrzavanja pretrage."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can use the following wildcards for file or folder names:"
msgstr "Možete koristiti sledeće džokere u imenima fajlova i fascikli:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Asterisk <quote><keycap>*</keycap></quote>"
msgstr "zvezdica (*)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The asterisk stands for any number of missing characters (even zero), that "
"means &eg; searching for <userinput>marc*</userinput> may find the files "
"<filename>marc</filename>, <filename>marc.png</filename> and <filename> "
"marc_must_not_read_this.kwd</filename>. <userinput>mar*.kwd</userinput> may "
"find <filename>marketplace.kwd</filename> and "
"<filename>marc_must_not_read_this.kwd</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Zvezdica zamenjuje proizvoljan broj bilo kojih znakova (čak i nijedan). Na "
"primer, potraga za <userinput>pera*</userinput> može naći fajlove "
"<filename>pera</filename>, <filename>pera.png</filename> i "
"<filename>pera_ne_sme_procitati_ovo.kwd</filename>, dok <userinput>per*.kwd</"
"userinput> može naći <filename>periskop.kwd</filename> i "
"<filename>pera_ne_sme_procitati_ovo.kwd</filename>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Question Mark <quote><keycap>?</keycap></quote>"
msgstr "znak pitanja (?)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In contrast to the asterisk, the question mark stands for exactly one "
"character, so <userinput>mar?</userinput> will find <filename>marc</"
"filename>, but <userinput>marc?</userinput> will not find anything, as our "
"files are called <filename>marc</filename> and <filename>marc.png</"
"filename>. You can put as many question marks in the term as you want, it "
"will find exactly that number of characters."
msgstr ""
"Nasuprot zvezdici, znak pitanja zamenjuje tačno jedan znak, pa će "
"<userinput>per?</userinput> naći <filename>pera</filename>, ali "
"<userinput>pera?</userinput> neće naći ništa, pošto se fajlovi zovu "
"<filename>pera</filename> i <filename>pera.png</filename>. U obrazac možete "
"staviti koliko hoćete znakova pitanja, što će poklopiti tačno toliko "
"proizvoljnih znakova."

# skip-rule: t-encoding
#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Character Set <quote>[...]</quote>"
msgstr "skup znakova ([...])"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "This matches any of the characters between the braces."
msgstr "Poklapa bilo koji od znakova u uglastim zagradama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Of course you can combine two or more wildcard symbols in a search term."
msgstr "Naravno, možete kombinovati više džokerskih simbola u istom obrascu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The results of your search will be displayed in the box below. A click with "
"the &RMB; on a selection in this box opens a context menu with a list of "
"actions for the selected files or folders."
msgstr ""
"Rezultati pretrage prikazuju se u polju ispod. Kliknite desnim na izbor u "
"ovom polju da dobijete kontekstni meni sa mogućim radnjama nad obuhvaćenim "
"fajlovima ili fasciklama."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Contents Tab"
msgstr "Jezičak <guilabel>Sadržaj</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "File type"
msgstr "Tip fajla:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can specify the type of file you are searching for."
msgstr "Ovde možete zadati tip traženog fajla."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Containing text"
msgstr "Sadrži tekst:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type in the word or phrase the files you are searching for must contain. "
"Note: If you do this in a large folder or checked <guilabel>Include "
"subfolders</guilabel> in the <guilabel>Name/Location</guilabel> tab, this "
"may take a long time."
msgstr ""
"Upišite reč ili izraz koji treba da sadrže traženi fajlovi. Napomena: ako "
"ovo zadate u velikoj fascikli, ili sa popunjenim <guilabel>Uključi "
"potfascikle</guilabel> pod jezičkom <guilabel>Ime/lokacija</guilabel>, "
"traženje može potrajati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option will <emphasis>not</emphasis> work for all files listed under "
"<guilabel>File type</guilabel>. Only the following file types are supported:"
msgstr ""
"Ova opcija <emphasis>neće</emphasis> funkcionisati za sve fajlove nabrojane "
"pod <guilabel>Tip fajla:</guilabel>. Podržani su samo sledeći tipovi fajlova:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text files, &eg; source code and <filename>README</filename> files"
msgstr ""
"tekstualni fajlovi, npr. izvorni kod i fajlovi <filename>README</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenOffice.org Writer / LibreOffice Writer"
msgstr "OpenOfficeov Pisac / LibreOfficeov Pisac"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenOffice.org Impress / LibreOffice Impress"
msgstr "OpenOfficeova Prezentacija / LibreOfficeova Prezentacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenOffice.org Calc / LibreOffice Calc"
msgstr "OpenOfficeov Račun / LibreOfficeov Račun"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calligra Words"
msgstr "<application>Calligrine Reči</application>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calligra Sheets"
msgstr "<application>Calligrini Listovi</application>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calligra Stage"
msgstr "<application>Calligrina Pozornica</application>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Case sensitive"
msgstr "Razlikuj veličinu slova"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enable this option, &kfind; will only find text in files with the "
"exact case matching, &eg; <userinput>MARC</userinput> will only match "
"<quote>MARC</quote>, not <quote>Marc</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Ako uključite ovu opciju, <application>K‑nalazač</application> će tražiti "
"tekst samo u fajlovima čija imena tačno poklapaju zadatu veličinu slova. Na "
"primer, <userinput>PERA</userinput> će poklopiti samo <filename>PERA</"
"filename>, a neće <filename>Pera</filename>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Regular expression"
msgstr "Regularni izraz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have installed the &kregexpeditor; tool from playground/utils on the "
"&kde; git server, you will have this additional option. Enabling it will "
"allow you to search for a <firstterm>regexp</firstterm> or regular "
"expression. A regexp is a way to specify conditions for your search, and "
"they can be very complex, and equally they can be very powerful. If you are "
"unfamiliar with regular expressions, you can choose <guibutton>Edit</"
"guibutton> button to open &kregexpeditor;. This tool allows you to construct "
"your set of conditions graphically, and then generates the expression for "
"you."
msgstr ""
"Ako je instalirana alatka <application>K‑uređivač-regiza</application> (iz "
"<filename class=\"directory\">playground/utils</filename> na "
"<application>git</application> serveru KDE‑a), imaćete i ovu opciju na "
"raspolaganju. Ako je uključite, obrazac za pretragu postaje "
"<emphasis>regularni izraz</emphasis> (skr. <firstterm>regiz</firstterm>). "
"Regularni izrazi su način pisanja uslova pretrage, koji mogu biti vrlo "
"složeni, ali zato i vrlo moćni. Ako vam regularni izrazi nisu poznati, "
"možete kliknuti na dugme <guibutton>Uređivanje</guibutton> da otvorite "
"<application>K‑uređivač-regiza</application>. Ova alatka omogućava da "
"grafički izgradite skup uslova, a zatim stvara izraz umesto vas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kregexpeditor; is a very useful tool, and can be used from within many "
"&kde; applications other than &kfind;. You can find more information from "
"within its own help file."
msgstr ""
"<application>K‑uređivač-regiza</application> je vrlo korisna alatka, koja se "
"pored <application>K‑nalazača</application> može koristiti u mnogim drugim "
"KDE programima. Više informacija naći ćete u okviru sopstvene pomoći "
"<application>K‑uređivača-regiza</application>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include binary files"
msgstr "Uključi binarne fajlove"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This lets you search in any type of file, even those that usually do not "
"contain text (for example program files and images)."
msgstr ""
"Aktivira traženje u svim tipovima fajlova, čak i onima koji obično ne sadrže "
"tekst (poput programa ili slika)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search metainfo sections"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These two fields can be used to search within files' specific comments or "
"metainfo."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here are some major cases:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Video files (avi, mp4, &etc;)</emphasis>: specify some tag "
"(<userinput>Bitrate</userinput>, <userinput>Duration</userinput>, &etc;) and "
"its value to find items which have the specified parameter value in their "
"metadata."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Images (png, jpeg, &etc;)</emphasis>: specify some tag "
"(<userinput>Width</userinput>, <userinput>Height</userinput>, &etc;) and its "
"value to find items which have the specified parameter value in their "
"metadata."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Audio files (mp3, flac, &etc;)</emphasis>: specify some tag "
"(<userinput>Title</userinput>, <userinput>Album</userinput>, &etc;) and its "
"value to find items which have the specified parameter value in their "
"metadata."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Ebooks (epub, azw, fb2, &etc;)</emphasis>: specify some tag "
"(<userinput>Title</userinput>, <userinput>Author</userinput>, &etc;) and its "
"value to find items which have the specified parameter value in their "
"metadata."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there is a translation of the tags into your language you can use the "
"localized tag names in the search criterion."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Properties Tab"
msgstr "Jezičak <guilabel>Svojstva</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can refine your search. These are the special refinements you can "
"choose:"
msgstr ""
"Ovde možete profiniti pretragu. Od posebnih profinjenja, možete izabrati:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find all files created or modified"
msgstr "Nađi sve fajlove stvorene ili izmenjene:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can either enter two dates, between which the files were created or "
"modified, or specify a time period."
msgstr ""
"Ovde možete ili uneti dva datuma između kojih su fajlovi bili stvoreni ili "
"izmenjeni, ili zadati vremenski period."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "File size is"
msgstr "Veličina fajla:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can specify if the file has to be at least or at most as big as the "
"size you entered in the following box, or else equal to the size."
msgstr ""
"Ovde možete zadati veličinu od koje fajl ne treba da bude veći ili manji, "
"ili kojoj treba da bude jednak."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Files owned by user</guilabel>, <guilabel>Files owned by group</"
"guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vlasnik fajlova:</guilabel>, <guilabel>Vlasnik je grupa:</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can specify user and group names as owner of the files."
msgstr "Ovde možete zadati korisničko ime i grupu koja je vlasnik fajlova."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credits and License"
msgstr "Zasluge i licenca"

