"<personname><firstname>Štefan</firstname> <surname>Kulov</surname></"
"personname> &Stephan.Kulow.mail;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Mario.Weilguni; &Mario.Weilguni.mail;"
